In March 2014, Ductos y Energéticos del None entered into a shareholders’ agreement to set up a joint venture, which is referred to as the TAG None joint venture, for the constmction and operation of the Los Ramones Norte pipeline project. In the same month, the TAG Nortejoint venture executed a 25-year natural gas ﬁrm transportation services agreement with Pemex TR_I t0 constmct and operate an approximately 452 km, 42-inch diameter pipeline with a design transportation capacity of 1,420 MMcfd (14.8 MMThd) and two compression stations.
